na niitowa na Kedolulaoma, mfalume wa Elamu, na Tidali, mfalume wa Goimu, na Amulafeli, mfalume wa Sinari, na Aliyoko, mfalume wa Elasari. Wafalume wane waitowa na wafalume watano.
