Bulahimu kakala na miyaka malongo manane na sita Hajili viyamwelile Ishmaeli.
Bulahimu viyakalile na miyaka malongo kenda na kenda, Mndewa kamulawilila na kamulongela, "Niye niiyo Mulungu yeli na Udaho. Genda haulongozi hangu na utende yanogile haulongozi hake.
